{"parse":{"title":"Ancient Monuments Preservation Act 1904","pageid":36546963,"revid":854731734,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">The Ancient Monuments Preservation Act, 1904</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Territorial extent</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/British_India\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"British India\">British India</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date assented to</th><td>\n18 March 1904</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>The Ancient Monuments Preservation Act, 1904</b> was passed in 18, March 1904 by <a href=\"/wiki/British_India\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"British India\">British India</a> during the times of <a href=\"/wiki/Lord_Curzon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord Curzon\">Lord Curzon</a>. It is expedient to provide for the preservation of ancient monuments, for the exercise of control over traffic in antiquities and over excavation in certain places, and for the protection and acquisition in certain cases of ancient monuments and of objects of archaeological, historical or artistic interest. Act preserves and restores ancient Indian monuments by <a href=\"/wiki/Archaeological_Survey_of_India\" title=\"Archaeological Survey of India\">Archaeological Survey of India</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Act_content\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Act content</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Sections\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sections</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Ancient_Monuments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ancient Monuments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Traffic_in_Antiquities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Traffic in Antiquities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Protection_of_Sculptures,_Carvings,_Images,_Bas-Reliefs,_Inscriptions_or_like_objects\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Protection of Sculptures, Carvings, Images, Bas-Reliefs, Inscriptions or like objects</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Archaeological_Excavation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Archaeological Excavation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#General\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">General</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Act_content\">Act content</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Act content\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sections\">Sections</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Sections\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Short title and extent.</li>\n<li>Definitions.</li>\n<li>Protected Monuments.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ancient_Monuments\">Ancient Monuments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Ancient Monuments\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Acquisition of rights in or guardianship of an ancient monument.</li>\n<li>Preservation of ancient monument by agreement.</li>\n<li>Owners under disability or not in possession.</li>\n<li>Enforcement of agreement.</li>\n<li>Purchasers at certain sales and persons claiming through owner bound by instrument executed by owner.</li>\n<li>Application of endowment to repair of an ancient monument.</li>\n<li>Compulsory purchase of ancient monument.</li>\n<li>Power of Central Government to control mining, etc., near ancient monument.</li>\n<li>Maintenance of certain protected monuments.</li>\n<li>Voluntary contributions.</li>\n<li>Protection of place of worship from misuse, pollution or desecration.</li>\n<li>Relinquishment of Government rights in a monument.</li>\n<li>Right of access to certain protected monuments.</li>\n<li>Penalties.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Traffic_in_Antiquities\">Traffic in Antiquities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Traffic in Antiquities\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Power to Central Government to control traffic in antiquities.</li></ol>\n<h3><span id=\"Protection_of_Sculptures.2C_Carvings.2C_Images.2C_Bas-Reliefs.2C_Inscriptions_or_like_objects\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Protection_of_Sculptures,_Carvings,_Images,_Bas-Reliefs,_Inscriptions_or_like_objects\">Protection of Sculptures, Carvings, Images, Bas-Reliefs, Inscriptions or like objects</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Protection of Sculptures, Carvings, Images, Bas-Reliefs, Inscriptions or like objects\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Power to Central Government to control moving of sculptures, carvings or like objects.</li>\n<li>Purchase of sculptures, carvings or like objects by the Government.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Archaeological_Excavation\">Archaeological Excavation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Archaeological Excavation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Power of Central Government to notify areas as protected.</li>\n<li>Power to enter upon and make excavations in a protected area.</li>\n<li>Power of Central government to make rules regulating archaeological excavation in protected areas.</li>\n<li>Power to acquire a protected area.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"General\">General</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: General\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Assessment of market value or compensation.</li>\n<li>Jurisdiction.</li>\n<li>Power to make rules.</li>\n<li>Protection to public servants acting under Act.</li></ol>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Ancient_Monuments_Preservation_Act_1904&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://asi.nic.in/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/5.pdf\">Text of the Act</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2180\nCached time: 20180918003747\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.056 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.075 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 429/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 1035/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 74/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 11/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 1/400\nLua time usage: 0.018/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 833 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   62.458      1 Template:Infobox_legislation\n100.00%   62.458      1 -total\n 76.19%   47.589      1 Template:Infobox\n 17.54%   10.956      1 Template:Infobox_legislation/images\n 14.53%    9.078      1 Template:Wikidata_image\n 11.51%    7.187      1 Template:Ifempty\n  4.14%    2.588      1 Template:Template_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:36546963-0!canonical and timestamp 20180918003747 and revision id 854731734\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"Archaeology_of_India"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Legislation_in_British_India"},{"sortkey":"","*":"1904_in_law"},{"sortkey":"","*":"1904_in_India"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Monuments_and_memorials_in_India"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Historic_preservation_legislation"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Historic_preservation_in_India"},{"sortkey":"","*":"1904_in_British_law"}],"links":[{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Archaeological Survey of India"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"British India"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Lord Curzon"}],"templates":[{"ns":10,"exists":"","*":"Template:Infob